file_content.text: It's completely shut down. Rude!
I can't get a comm signal to the others. We need to find a way back to them.
We must warn our friends.
Good thing you brought the galaxy's greatest escape artist with you.
Forget it. The longer we stay, the better the odds we become permanent residents.
This was a dead end.
Point taken, but we can't go back that way, so...
I refuse to die here. Find an exit, or I'll make one myself--using you as a battering ram.
Make yourself useful, or else.
Me? You're the hard-headed one in this relationship.
I'm not Quinn. I don't need threats for motivation.
Gosh, when you put it like that, I feel extra motivated.
Here, tunnel, tunnel, tunnel...
You underestimate your enemies. They are survivors.
I command legions.
Numbers are irrelevant.
Your logic circuits are corrupted, and you passed that corruption to the GEMINIs. They are as much a threat to Iokath as you.
I will recycle your components into something more useful.
There has been an error.
Yes. Yours. I escaped while you were distracted, but I promise we will meet again. Soon.
I think this leads back to the gang.
I trust your instincts. We'll get through this together.
I have faith in your skills.
That's why you're going in first.
I was hoping for something better than a guess, Vette.
Don't think. Be certain.
This ain't my first tomb, you know.
Good work, Vette. You've earned your continued survival.
Congratulations, you survive.
I finally get you and Kaliyo as a couple.
I used to do this for money. Now, it's for compliments like that.
After you...
